OL,3,CThe welsh boxer banned from competing
OL,4,Cfor British title because he was black
OL,6,FThe story of an Olympic boxer from
OL,7,FMerthyr Tydfil who faced racism has
OL,8,Fbeen turned into a stage show by a
OL,9,FWelsh theatre production company.
OL,11,FIt will tell the true story of
OL,12,FCuthbert Taylor who was denied the
OL,13,Fright to compete for the British title
OL,14,Fin 1928 due to the colour of his skin.
OL,16,FTheatr na nOg in Neath is putting on
OL,17,Fthe production for more than 5,000
OL,18,Fschool children from September to
OL,19,FNovember.
