OL,3,CThe welsh boxer banned from competing
OL,4,Cfor British title because he was black
OL,6,FSimeon Desvignes who plays Cuthbert in
OL,7,F"The Fight", said: "I'm sure Cuthbert
OL,8,FTaylor is not the only one who went
OL,9,Fthrough this back in the 1920s,
OL,10,Fthere's lots of other mixed race or
OL,11,Fblack boxers that also had the same
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"In this day and age when you've got
OL,15,Fheavyweight title contenders like
OL,16,FDaniel Dubois and Anthony Joshua that
OL,17,Fare competing for heavyweight titles,
OL,18,FI'm thinking about how far boxing has
OL,19,Fprogressed since then."
